cimg|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
cimg: cimg (C++ Template Image Processing Library)
cimg:
cimg: The CImg Library is an open-source C++ library for image processing.
cimg: It provides a minimal set of C++ classes that can be used to perform
cimg: several common operations on generic images (up to 4D multivalued
cimg: ones). It is simple-to-use, efficient, and portable. It's a really
cimg: pleasant  toolkit for developing image processing stuffs in C++.
cimg:
cimg: http://cimg.eu/
